5A39A25C.Line1.9118B: Bah, I’ll be fine...just wore myself out. Packing to visit my neighbors.

8E229560.Line5.9118B: They’ve got it worse than me, poor souls. Infected, forsaken...left to wander the swamp until it takes them.

F42E1BDE.Line3.9118B: Since you’re here, help an old woman...take these supplies to Baridan, Duraya, and Raldin. Treat them kindly, or the swamp will hear of it.

FD2BFB8D.VoiceDir5.9118B: Sad sympathy, but it is what it is.
